      "finding_b": "risk-004",
      "description": "Requirement for multi-tenant data isolation conflicts with the identified security risk of current application-level row filtering.",
      "resolution": "Remediate the data isolation model by implementing schema or database-level separation to meet compliance requirements.",
      "reasoning": "This resolution ensures that the requirement for data isolation aligns with security compliance, reducing the risk flagged."
    },
